---
title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Pork Chorizo Patties with Tomato, Charred Corn and Spinach Salad
description: Shake up dinnertime with a loaded, smart salad of savoury, Mexican-spiced pork chorizo patties, spinach, tomatoes, charred corn and, of course, tangy ranch to tie it all together!
